tool_description: Major golf tours, fixtures, results and up to the minute leaderboard data to enhance your applications.
title: Golf Leaderboard Data

api_list.name: PGA Scorecards
api_list.description: Provides scorecards for a given player in a given tournament
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://golf-leaderboard-data.p.rapidapi.com/scorecard/{tourn_id}/{player_id}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "golf-leaderboard-data.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())

meta.description: Displays full scorecard for given player in given tournament
meta.title: Scorecard for Carlos Ortiz - Vivint Houston Open

api_list.name: Leaderboard
api_list.description: Lists information for a given tournament_id. Includes leaderboard and per player round information. Also includes live tournament status.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://golf-leaderboard-data.p.rapidapi.com/leaderboard/{tournament_id}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "golf-leaderboard-data.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())

meta.description: Golf Leaderboard including current leaderboard and round scores

leaderboard_array.position: Integer - ignore if 0, position in tournament

rounds_array.course_number: Integer - course to which round relates
rounds_array.tee_time_local: String - tee time in tournament timezone

leaderboard_array.status: String - active, cut, retired, wd=withdrawn, dsq=disqualified
leaderboard_array.strokes: Integer - total strokes across all rounds - updated on completion of each round, default = 0
leaderboard_array.total_to_par: String - player score over all rounds completed

live_details.total_rounds: Integer - total number of rounds in competition

tournament_object.name: String
tournament_object.type: String - Stroke Play or Match Play - determines how to display leaderboard results.

meta.title: Golf Leaderboard - PGA Championship
